subdivision_of_building: VACANT SITE, OPPOSITE CENTRAL VENTURE PA
description: Redevelopment of existing site to provide a residential development comprising the erection of two x 9-storey buildings and 2 x 5 storey buildings on either side of re-aligned Cronin Street, providing 109 residential dwellings (100% Affordable) , 10 no. car parking space together with access, hard and soft landscaping and other associated works incidental to the development.
